title: Cespedes On NLDS: ‘I Am 100 Percent Ready To Start This Battle’
text: Cespedes On NLDS: ‘I Am 100 Percent Ready To Start This Battle’ Tuesday, 6 October 2015 (6 minutes ago) The Mets' star outfielder was hit by a pitch on his left hand last week, but that won't limit him in the National League Division Series against the Dodgers.
